@startuml
' Jornada completa de envios - visão macro do fluxo feliz.
title 00 - Jornada de Envios - Fluxo Feliz Macro

autonumber
actor Buyer as Comprador
participant "Marketplace Web" as FE
participant "Marketplace BFF" as BFF
participant "Product Search Service" as Search
participant "Product Catalog Service" as Catalog
participant "Shipping Promise Service" as Promise
participant "Checkout Service" as Checkout
participant "Order Service" as Order
participant "Inventory Service" as Inventory
participant "Fulfillment Center Service" as FC
participant "Routing Service" as Routing
participant "Carrier Service" as Carrier
participant "Shipping Pricing Service" as Pricing
participant "Shipment Service" as Shipment
participant "Tracking Service" as Tracking
participant "Notification Service" as Notification
queue "Kafka" as Kafka

Comprador -> FE: Pesquisa produto
FE -> BFF: GET /api/web/v1/products/search?query={texto}
BFF -> Search: GET /v1/products/search?query={texto}
Search --> BFF: Produtos paginados
BFF --> FE: Cards de produto

Comprador -> FE: Seleciona produto e informa CEP
FE -> BFF: GET /api/web/v1/products/{skuId}/page?zipCode={cep}
BFF -> Catalog: GET /products/{skuId}
BFF -> Promise: POST /shipping-promises/
Promise -> Catalog: POST /products/physical-info/batch
Promise -> Inventory: POST /inventory/availability/batch
Promise -> FC: POST /fulfillment-centers/candidates/search
Promise -> Routing: POST /routes/search
Promise -> Carrier: POST /carrier-availability/search
Promise -> Pricing: POST /shipping-prices/quotes/batch
Promise --> BFF: Promessa disponível
BFF --> FE: Página de produto com frete

Comprador -> FE: Confirma compra
FE -> BFF: POST /api/web/v1/checkouts/ + Idempotency-Key
BFF -> Checkout: POST /checkouts + Idempotency-Key
Checkout -> Promise: POST /shipping-promises/
Checkout --> BFF: Checkout criado
BFF --> FE: Checkout criado

FE -> BFF: POST /api/web/v1/checkouts/{checkoutId}/confirm
BFF -> Checkout: POST /checkouts/{checkoutId}/confirm
Checkout -> Kafka: CheckoutConfirmedIntegrationEvent
Kafka -> Order: Consome CheckoutConfirmedIntegrationEvent
Order -> Kafka: ReserveInventoryCommand
Order -> Kafka: ReserveFulfillmentCapacityCommand
Kafka -> Inventory: Reserva estoque
Kafka -> FC: Reserva capacidade
Inventory -> Kafka: InventoryReservedIntegrationEvent
FC -> Kafka: FulfillmentCapacityReservedIntegrationEvent
Kafka -> Order: Confirma reservas recebidas
Order -> Kafka: AuthorizePaymentCommand
Order -> Kafka: ConfirmInventoryReservationCommand
Order -> Kafka: ConfirmFulfillmentCapacityCommand
Order -> Kafka: CreateShipmentCommand
Kafka -> Shipment: Cria shipment
Shipment -> Carrier: Booking / geração de etiqueta
Carrier --> Shipment: Tracking code + label
Shipment -> Kafka: ShipmentCreatedIntegrationEvent
Kafka -> Tracking: Cria projeção de tracking
Kafka -> Notification: Notifica shipment criado
Notification --> Comprador: Push/e-mail/SMS

@enduml
